OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBill Turnbull: Classic FM  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpresenter steps back from  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fradio show for health      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Classic FM presenter Bill Turnbull has 
OL,6, announced "with great regret" that he  
OL,7, is to take a leave of absence from his 
OL,8, radio show for "health reasons".       
OL,10,FThe former BBC Breakfast host was      
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with prostate cancer in 2017.
OL,13,F"The road has been a bit bumpy recently
OL,14,Fand I need to take some time to focus  
OL,15,Fon getting better," he tweeted on      
OL,16,FThursday, promising to return.         
OL,18,F"I'm sorry to do this, as I absolutely 
OL,19,Flove doing the programme, and have     
OL,20,Fhugely enjoyed the past five years."   
